{"tid":2458273,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"西貢村屋變大麻種植場 海關機場截毒郵包據收貨地址拘藝人吳耀漢女兒","createTime":"2021-03-23T09:50:50.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-25T12:46:50.000Z","uid":117837,"like":46,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"214562d152d68b093ba8aca9f74ffbd96e92dc6b","tid":2458273,"uid":117837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T09:50:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/0TJiYe4Y9l3AHbO8OvWun8oyNio=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/UY4DMBI2VZB7VAQZXMZTN5S7PY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F0TJiYe4Y9l3AHbO8OvWun8oyNio%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FUY4DMBI2VZB7VAQZXMZTN5S7PY.jpg&h=4a8e031e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港海關毒品調查科人員今午到西貢南圍村進行掃毒，並拘捕一名女子，據知該人為52歲吳耀漢女兒，涉及一宗毒品案。<br />\n<br />\n消息指，海關早前於香港國際機場檢查一個空運郵包時，發現內藏大麻，其後根據收貨地址，今午掩至西貢南圍村部署埋伏行動。大約4至5名便衣海關於下午近2時抵達西貢南圍村一村屋，之後在門外拉起封鎖線阻止其他人靠近。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210323/DOKZGZR76VFJ5AFZJW5YR644NA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210323%2FDOKZGZR76VFJ5AFZJW5YR644NA%2F&d=9ZLePgUN12BIej1hBtk97ZggdM0W6%2BkgeusliPwa7Y4%3D&h=ad93c7d3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210323%2FDOKZGZR76VFJ5AFZJW5YR644NA%2F&h=980ad11e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210323/DOKZGZR76VFJ5AFZJW5YR644NA/</a>"},{"pid":"c8fd8489aff33f9f471e364dbb914e48271eafe5","tid":2458273,"uid":117837,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T09:51:31.000Z","msg":"藍屍都拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57d5f08a3e1de1a38e8d010550da527b